Pyrana - python package for simple manipulation of multimedia files
===================================================================

CAUTION:
--------

pyrana itself is licensed under the MIT license.
However, it links to the ffmpeg libraries which, depending on the
build configuration, can be LGPL or GPL.
As result, the whole package will become LGPL or GPL.
Check the license of the libraries you're currently using.

